  <brief_title>A Safety and Efficacy Comparison of BLI4700 Bowel Prep Versus an FDA-approved Comparator in Adults Prior to Colonoscopy</brief_title>
  <official_title>BLI4700-301: A Safety and Efficacy Comparison of BLI4700 Bowel Preparation Versus an FDA-approved Comparator in Adult Subjects Prior to Colonoscopy</official_title>
